name: Public
description: A member of the general public.

name: Application
description: The player has applied to join Ozraid. Their application is pending review by an Ozraid Raid Leader or Administrator.

name: Member
description: The player is an Ozraid member.

name: Author
description: The player is an Ozraid member who has access to the website Admin Page to write articles.

name: Editor
description: The player is an Ozraid member who has access to the website Admin Page to write and edit articles.

name: Raid Leader
description: The player is an Ozraid Raid Leader who has access to multiple website Admin Page functions.

name: Administrator
description: The player is an Ozraid Raid Leader or member who has access to all website Admin Page functions.
